  <name>AppCenter</name>
  <summary>Browse and manage apps</summary>
  <description>
    <p>The open source, pay-what-you-want app store from elementary. Reviewed and curated by elementary to ensure a native, privacy-respecting, and secure experience. Browse by categories or search and discover new apps. AppCenter is also used for updating your system to the latest and greatest version for new features and fixes.</p>
  </description>
  <releases>
    <release version="3.10.0" date="2021-12-10" urgency="medium">
      <description>
        <p>New features:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Added an option to automatically update curated apps</li>
          <li>Warn when apps are built against older runtimes</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Fixes:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Prevent back button from disappearing or requiring multiple clicks</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Improvements:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Show screenshot captions in a tooltip</li>
          <li>Updated translations</li>
        </ul>
      </description>
    </release>
